{"tid":850683,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月新番]FAIRY TAIL 魔導少年 妖精的尾巴 フェアリーテイル 最終季集中討論","createTime":"2018-10-06T16:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T22:16:58.000Z","uid":3020,"like":12,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7395bb32b364fad854418e876a9fd65b932941","tid":850683,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPRC6V2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPRC6V2.jpg&h=df173748&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介<br />\n故事描述，「魔導士公會」是個為魔導士們仲介各式工作的地方，而以成為獨當一面的魔導士為目標的少女「露西」，一直憧憬著加入擁有眾多厲害魔法師雲集的公會「妖精尾巴」。她在操縱火的魔導士「納茲」的引導下順利加入了妖精尾巴 ，並在認識了許多高手之後，與納茲等人組成了隊伍展開冒險。<br />\n<br />\n官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/fairytail/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tv-tokyo.co.jp%2Fanime%2Ffairytail%2F&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93np4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ff95f298\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tv-tokyo.co.jp/anime/fairytail/</a><br />\n<br />\n1~<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42660-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-42660-1-1.html&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93np4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=3ab9ffbd\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-42660-1-1.html</a><br />\n1~<br />\n<a href=\"http://fenglin.to/84493/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffenglin.to%2F84493%2F&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93np4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=9c754fff\" target=\"_blank\">http://fenglin.to/84493/</a><br />\n<br />\n10月7日起 星期日 06:00直播<br />\n<a href=\"https://mov3.co/en/tvtokyo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Fen%2Ftvtokyo%2F&d=bbj2SoGVaOb6bYcrjj93np4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e507608f\" target=\"_blank\">https://mov3.co/en/tvtokyo/</a><br />\n<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DDXd4o_XBeE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fww